para_trans: It's close to fun. , T. Regarding sanction of 30 bedded rural hospital at Paranda, District Dharashiv as a special case.
Government Decision No: Establishment-2024 / P.No.212 / Health-4
Read: - Letter No. of Joint Director, Health Services, Mumbai: By J. No. / Room 3 / T-2 / No. No.99876 / Grade / Near / Pashama / 9783-85 Date 29.04.2024.

Preface: Close to the fun. , T. The matter of sanctioning a rural hospital at Paranda, District Dharashiv was under consideration of the Government. The following decisions are being taken in this regard:
Government Decision: - Not close to the moment. , T. A 30-bed rural hospital is being sanctioned as a special case at Paranda, District Dharashiv.
This Government decision will be made available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
